trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> can contain two kinds of objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the activity associated with the activity status event; and, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects specify member data to be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>두 종류의 개체를 포함할 수 있습니다: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>개체는 활동 상태 이벤트와 연결 된 활동에서 추출할 멤버 데이터를 지정 하 고, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>개체는 워크플로의 루트 활동에서 추출할 멤버 데이터를 지정 합니다.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Both of these extract types can also specify annotations to be returned with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: 두 추출 형식이 추출한 데이터와 함께 반환 될 주석도 지정할 수 있습니다.
